    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "The Node API for GRPC is only callback based. But you can use [promisifyAll()](bluebirdjs.com/docs/api/promise.promisifyall.html) from [bluebird library](https://www.npmjs.com/package/bluebird) to create a promised based version of your grpc methods:\n\n``` javascript\nconst bluebird = require('bluebird');\n// Cb style\nconst clientCb = require('grpc').client;\nclientCb({}, function cb(result) {});\n// Promise style\nconst client = bluebird.promisifyAll(client);\nclient.sayHelloAsync({}).then((result) => {});\n```\n"
  },
